<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>PSG College of Technology - Final Semester Internship</title>
<style>
  @page {
    size: A4;
    margin: 12mm 16mm 10mm 16mm;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    color: #000;
    line-height: 1.3;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .page {
    width: 100%;
    page-break-after: always;
  }
  .page:last-child {
    page-break-after: avoid;
  }

  /* ── College header ── */
  .college-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .college-name {
    font-size: 11pt;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .form-title {
    font-size: 10pt;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  /* ── Date line ── */
  .date-line {
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    margin-bottom: 1px;
  }

  /* ── Paragraphs ── */
  p {
    margin: 2px 0;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* ── Tables ── */
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 3px 0;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
  }
  td, th {
    border: 1px solid #000;
    padding: 2px 4px;
    vertical-align: top;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  th {
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 8pt;
  }
  .no-border td {
    border: none;
    padding: 0 2px;
  }

  /* ── Lists ── */
  ol {
    margin: 2px 0 2px 16px;
    padding: 0;
  }
  ol li {
    font-size: 8.8pt;
    margin-bottom: 1px;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  ol.alpha { list-style-type: lower-alpha; margin-left: 20px; }

  /* ── Utility ── */
  .small { font-size: 8pt; }
  .italic { font-style: italic; }
  .bold { font-weight: bold; }
  .center { text-align: center; }
  .right { text-align: right; }
  .underline { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* ── Sig lines p2 ── */
  .sig-cell {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    border-top: 1px solid #000 !important;
    border-left: none !important;
    border-right: none !important;
    border-bottom: none !important;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .page-footer { text-align: center; font-size: 8.5pt; margin-top: 4px; }
  .pto { text-align: right; font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: bold; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══════════════ PAGE 1 ═══════════════ -->
<div class="page">

  <div class="college-header">
    <div class="college-name">PSG COLLEGE OF TECHNOLOGY, COIMBATORE 641 004</div>
    <div class="form-title">Undertaking for Pursuing Internship in the Final Semester (UG/PG)</div>
  </div>

  <table class="no-border" style="margin:1px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:50%;">From</td>
      <td style="width:50%; text-align:right;"><strong>Date:</strong> {{currentDate}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p>{{student_name}}</p>
  <p>{{roll_number}}</p>

  <p style="margin-top:4px;">To</p>
  <p>The Principal</p>
  <p>PSG College of Technology</p>
  <p>Coimbatore – 641004</p>

  <p style="margin-top:2px;">Through: THE HEAD OF THE DEPARTMENT, DEPARTMENT OF {{department}}</p>

  <p style="margin-top:2px;">Dear Sir,</p>

  <p><strong>Sub:</strong> Undertaking while pursuing Internship/Project Work II in Industry / Institutions.</p>

  <p>I wish to inform that, I have been offered internship in the organization, details of which are provided below. The activities carried out during this internship will be adequate for completing Project Work II/Code.............. ) as per the recommendations of the Guide and the project review committee.</p>

  <!-- Internship details table -->
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:25%;">Name &amp; Address of the<br>Industry / Institution</th>
        <th colspan="2">Internship Period</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:21%;">Guide from the<br>Industry / Institution<br>with contact details</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:10%;">Guide in the<br>department</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:11%;">Stipend<br>receivable (if any)</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:9%;">From (date)</th>
        <th style="width:9%;">To (Date)</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td style="height:36px;">{{company_name}}<br>{{company_address}}<br>{{company_city}}{{#if company_state}}, {{company_state}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{start_date}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{end_date}}</td>
        <td>{{guide_name_industry}}<br>{{guide_contact}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;"></td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{#if stipend_amount}}₹ {{stipend_amount}}{{else}}NIL{{/if}}</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>I request you to permit me to accept the offer of internship and provide attendance for the duration mentioned.</p>
  <p><strong>I hereby undertake the following.</strong></p>

  <ol>
    <li>I will be regular and sincere in carrying out my internship at the above organization and I will obey the Rules and Regulations of the organization.</li>
    <li>My attendance will be sent regularly to my department by the Industry / Institution.</li>
    <li>I will update the guide in the college regularly through reports reviewed by the guide in the industry.</li>
    <li>I will attend all the project work II reviews scheduled in the department and submit the report for my Project Work II on or before the deadline specified by the Department.</li>
    <li>I have completed all course work except Project Work II to become eligible for the award of the Degree.</li>
    <li>I have 1 / 2 final semester elective course/s for which I have registered along with other students. I will study the courses under self study mode and I will appear for all CA Evaluation Tests/Tutorials in the above courses.</li>
    <li>I am aware of internship and conversion to full time offer and I will abide by the rules of Placement &amp; Training Office.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed the offer letter for internship.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed my parent's permission letter to carry out the internship/Project work.</li>
    <li>*I am not in receipt of any other scholarship/Stipend from the company (Applicable to PG AICTE GATE Scholarship PG NON GATE State Government Scholarship Students).</li>
    <li>*If I intend to receive stipend from the company, I am aware that, I will not be eligible to receive the PG Scholarship receiving from AICTE /State Government during the period of my paid internship.</li>
  </ol>

  <p class="small">Strike out if not applicable.<br>
  * PG GATE Student has to produce a letter from the company in their letter head to this effect.</p>

  <p class="small italic">Note: Do not alter the format</p>

  <!-- Page 1 bottom sig row -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin-top:10px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:30%;">Tutor/Programme Co-ordinator</td>
      <td style="width:20%; text-align:center;">Guide</td>
      <td style="width:20%; text-align:center;">HoD</td>
      <td style="width:30%; text-align:right;">(Signature of the Student)</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="page-footer">Page 1/2</div>
  <div class="pto">(PTO)</div>

</div><!-- end page 1 -->


<!-- ═══════════════ PAGE 2 ═══════════════ -->
<div class="page">

  <div class="college-header">
    <div class="college-name">PSG COLLEGE OF TECHNOLOGY, COIMBATORE 641 004</div>
  </div>

  <p class="center underline bold" style="font-size:10pt; margin:4px 0 6px 0;">Recommendation from the department</p>

  <p><strong>Academic details of the student:</strong></p>

  <table class="no-border" style="margin:2px 0 4px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:8%;"><strong>NAME:</strong></td>
      <td style="width:40%;">{{student_name}}</td>
      <td style="width:18%; text-align:right;"><strong>Roll Number:</strong></td>
      <td style="width:34%;">{{roll_number}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td></td><td></td>
      <td style="text-align:right;"><strong>CGPA:</strong></td>
      <td>{{cgpa}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- Academic status table -->
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:20%;">Number of Pending Redo courses with Course Code &amp; Title</th>
        <th style="width:20%;">Number of courses with Course Code</th>
        <th style="width:20%;">Number of Pending RA courses with Course Code A Title</th>
        <th style="width:22%;">Pending Courses of current semester with Course Code &amp; Title</th>
        <th style="width:18%;">REMARKS</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr style="height:40px;">
        <td>{{#if redo_courses}}{{redo_courses}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td></td>
        <td>{{#if ra_courses}}{{ra_courses}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td>{{#if pending_courses}}{{pending_courses}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td></td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="height:25px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:25px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:25px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:25px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top:4px;">The work assigned by the industry /institution <strong>meets</strong> the academic standards for Project Work II.<br>
  This student has not accepted any other internship.</p>

  <p style="margin-top:3px; font-size:8.8pt;">*This student has accepted another internship but has declined the same due to academic/ health/ financial reasons. The company/institutions is informed of his inability to accept the offer through letter/email. The details of the organization is given below.</p>

  <!-- Declined internship table -->
  <table style="margin-top:3px;">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:28%;">Name &amp; Address of the<br>Industry / Institution</th>
        <th colspan="2">Internship Period</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:24%;">Guide from the<br>Industry / institution<br>with contact details</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:12%;">Guide in the<br>department</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:11%;">From (date)</th>
        <th style="width:11%;">To (Date)</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr style="height:35px;">
        <td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top:4px;">This student can be permitted to accept the internship and complete Project Work II within the specified time period.</p>

  <!-- Sig row 1 -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin-top:32px;">
    <tr>
      <td class="sig-cell" style="width:22%;">Tutor/Programme Coordinator</td>
      <td style="width:3%; border:none;"></td>
      <td class="sig-cell" style="width:17%;">Guide</td>
      <td style="width:3%; border:none;"></td>
      <td class="sig-cell" style="width:17%;">HoD</td>
      <td style="width:3%; border:none;"></td>
      <td class="sig-cell" style="width:35%;">Dean, Placement &amp; Training</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- Sig row 2 -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin-top:28px;">
    <tr>
      <td class="sig-cell" style="width:40%;">Dean - Academic</td>
      <td style="width:10%; border:none;"></td>
      <td class="sig-cell" style="width:50%;">Principal</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p class="small" style="margin-top:5px;">*Strike out if not applicable.</p>

  <!-- NOTE -->
  <p style="margin-top:5px; font-size:9pt;"><strong>NOTE:</strong></p>
  <ol style="margin:1px 0 0 16px;">
    <li style="font-size:8.8pt;">Original Form shall be submitted to <strong>Placement Office</strong> and Photo copies shall be submitted to
      <ol class="alpha" style="margin:0 0 0 16px;">
        <li style="font-size:8.8pt;">Academic section</li>
        <li style="font-size:8.8pt;">Concerned Department</li>
      </ol>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <div class="page-footer" style="margin-top:6px;">Page 2/2</div>

</div><!-- end page 2 -->

</body>
</html>
